<h2>Manuscript Submission</h2>
<p>We strongly encourage authors to submit a presubmission inquiry before making a full submission. To submit a presubmission inquiry, please log into the <em>PLOS Biology</em> online submission system and select "Submit New Manuscript" from your homepage, and then choose the "Presubmission Inquiry" article type.</p>

<p>Submit manuscripts online at <a href="http://www.editorialmanager.com/pbiology/" title="PLOS Biology Online Manuscript Submission System">http://www.editorialmanager.com/pbiology/</a>.</p>

